&quot;Error&quot; for bitmap &quot;0,16&quot;</p><p class="MsoNormal">  Location:          odls_default_module.c:551</p><p class="MsoNormal">--------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><div><span style="color:rgb(31,73,125)"> </span><br></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color:rgb(31,73,125)">This happens
